				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$k = 10, 12, 14$$\end{document}k=10,12,14). On the other hand, in the strongly clustered regime \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
